                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <lb/>
                     <label>Inscriptions:</label> The <locus from="ia" to="ia">right flyleaf a side (f. ia)</locus> bears the title and author in a bold nasta‘līq hand.
                     <lb/>
                     <label>Bookplates:</label> <locus from="Inner_back_cover" to="Inner_back_cover">Left pastedown</locus>: <q xml:lang="en">Bibliotheca
                        Lindesiana</q> with pencilled shelfmark <q xml:lang="en">1/E</q>, and <q xml:lang="en">Hamilton MSS
