                  <provenance><p>After his death, the
                     <orgName type="standard" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/134857252">British Museum</orgName> selected 352 volumes from his collection of over a thousand Indian and Persian manuscripts, now held in the
                     <orgName type="standard" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/121814978">British Library</orgName>.</p>
